Record Class ConversionResult.Failure<T>

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
io.github.kaktushose.proteus.conversion.ConversionResult.Failure<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the result
Record Components:
errorType - the ConversionResult.Failure.ErrorType of this failed conversion
message - an error message describing the failed conversion
context - the ConversionResult.ConversionContext, can be null if this ConversionResult.Failure wasn't created during conversion, e.g. if no path was found
All Implemented Interfaces:
ConversionResult<T>
Enclosing interface:
ConversionResult<T>
public static record ConversionResult.Failure<T>(@NotNull ConversionResult.Failure.ErrorType errorType, @NotNull String message, @Nullable ConversionResult.ConversionContext context) extends Record implements ConversionResult<T>
Implementation of ConversionResult that indicates a failed conversion.
